description: Garage parking and a roof deck! This unit checks every box! This beautiful condo has been tastefully updated and has all the bells and whistles, including fireplace, washer and dryer in unit, central AC, roof deck and garage parking. Primary bedroom has a walk through closet into the newly renovated full bathroom. Second bedroom perfect for guests or home office. Fits a queen and a desk comfortably. Half bath off the hall with a full sized washer and dryer. Open concept kitchen with bar seating flows into the living room complete with gas fireplace. In the warmer months, enjoy your roof deck with friends. Garage parking for one car, can fit a SUV. Deeded storage in basement. This unit is leased until 8/31/25.
